OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,F"I've turned it off", Acting Chief
OL,7,FConstable Scott Green on how the West
OL,8,FMidlands Police will use AI after the
OL,9,Fcontroversy surrounding the Maccabi
OL,10,FTel Aviv Aston Villa match.
OL,12,FThe acting Chief Constable of West
OL,13,FMidlands Police says he's temporarily
OL,14,Fpaused use of an Artificial
OL,15,FIntelligence while investigations into
OL,16,Fthe force continue.
OL,18,FIn his first interview with ITV News
OL,19,FCentral, Scott Green says officers
OL,20,Fhave been using the technology for a
OL,21,Flong time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FBut its use came under scrutiny when
OL,7,Fit was revealed that it had produced
OL,8,Ffalse information about Maccabi Tel
OL,9,FAviv fans, before they were banned
OL,10,Ffrom attending a match against Aston
OL,11,FVilla last year.
OL,13,FScott Green was appointed as acting
OL,14,FChief Constable after his predecessor
OL,15,Fretired, following criticism of his
OL,16,Fforce's decision to ban fans of the
OL,17,FIsraeli club.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FHe says one of the first things he did
OL,7,Fin the post was refer the force to the
OL,8,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct
OL,9,Fto review their handling of the match.
OL,11,FThe decision, made by the Birmingham
OL,12,FSafety Advisory Group, came under
OL,13,Fintense political scrutiny, with the
OL,14,Fformer Chief Constable Craig Guillford
OL,15,Fquestioned by the Home Affairs select
OL,16,Fcommittee.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FIn a statement, Craig Guildford, 52,
OL,7,Fsaid the "political and media frenzy"
OL,8,Faround his position had become
OL,9,F"detrimental" to the force, and he
OL,10,Fannounced his retirement.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said he
OL,13,Fhad "done the right thing" by
OL,14,F"stepping down" as Chief Constable.
OL,16,FThe new chief said West Midlands
OL,17,FPolice has used lots of different
OL,18,Fforms of AI for a long time and will
OL,19,Fcontinue to do so, but says they have
OL,20,Fnow stopped using AI, especially
OL,21,FMicrosoft Co-Pilot.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@eO]qD@AOUqD@MO]uD@EOUuD@ZO]vD@
OL,26,AAOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
