OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FCo-Pilot is an AI that is part of the
OL,7,FMicrosoft Suite of software, like Word
OL,8,Fand Excel.
OL,10,FIt was blamed for hallucinating a
OL,11,Fmatch between West Ham and Maccabi Tel
OL,12,FAviv, which was used to support the
OL,13,Fdecision to ban fans of the Israeli
OL,14,Fclub from the Europa League match
OL,15,Fagainst Aston Villa.
OL,17,FMr Green said that he would wait to
OL,18,Fgive officers the green light to use
OL,19,FCo-Pilot again after the IOPC report
OL,20,Ffindings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FIn response to further questioning, Mr
OL,7,FGreen said he couldn't go into detail
OL,8,Fabout the policing of the Maccabi Tel
OL,9,FAviv-Aston Villa match, because it was
OL,10,Fbeing investigated by the police
OL,11,Fwatchdog.
OL,13,FDespite recent scandals, the acting
OL,14,FChief Constable says the force is
OL,15,Fperforming "really well" overall.
OL,17,FHe said across the last 12 months,
OL,18,Fthere have been "22,000 fewer victims
OL,19,Fof crime", and knife crime and
OL,20,Fneighbourhood crime are "falling".
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@XO]zD@QOU{D@IO]|D@YOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
