CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police's key priorities
OL,8,FScott Green also laid out his key
OL,9,Fpriorities for the West Midlands
OL,10,FPolice:
OL,12,FWho is Scott Green?
OL,14,FPCC Simon Foster announced on the 16th
OL,15,FJanuary that he had appointed Scott
OL,16,FGreen as Acting Chief Constable of
OL,17,FWest Midlands Police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FHe started his career with South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police in the 1990s and rose
OL,8,Fto the rank of Chief Superintendent,
OL,9,Fserving as the district commander for
OL,10,FBarnsley.
OL,12,FMr Green then served as Assistant
OL,13,FChief Constable of Staffordshire
OL,14,FPolice in 2020 and then joined the
OL,15,Fleadership team at Greater Manchester
OL,16,FPolice in 2021. Two years later, he
OL,17,Fbecame Deputy Chief Constable of West
OL,18,FMidlands Police.
OL,20,FHe is also a fellow of the Royal
OL,21,FSociety of Arts.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1772745124
OL,3,CWest Midlands Police boss 'turns off'
OL,4,CAI that caused Maccabi Tel Aviv error
OL,6,FScott Green, in turn, has appointed
OL,7,FJen Mattinson to be Acting Deputy
OL,8,FChief Constable.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police said: "As the
OL,11,FActing Chief Constable of West
OL,12,FMidlands Police and responsible for
OL,13,Fthe force's performance, he is proud
OL,14,Fto have been part of the chief officer
OL,15,Fteam that led WMP out of 'Special
OL,16,FMeasures' in an unprecedented nine
OL,17,Fmonths and 27 days ` now the fastest
OL,18,Fof any police force."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
